Scott Pittman ya hana Allan McGregor na Rangers da ke da rikici, wanda ya ƙare Lithgow a cikin kullun daga wani wasa na Livingston.
An yi ta yin ta-da-ka-da-ka a filin wasa na Livingston da kuma kulob din, kuma ba a yi watsi da hukuncin da aka yanke ba - bayan da Halkett ya yi nasara a kan Glenn Middleton, da kuma daya don buga kwallon.
