Trump ya kamata ya yi magana a wannan makon game da zargin da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka yi wa zargin cewa ya yi aiki da lalata, kuma ya yi watsi da kuri'un tabbatar da Sanata na tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Amma babban manufar wannan taron na jam'iyyun jam'iyyun shine don taimakawa 'yan Republican su sami goyon baya kafin zaben watan Nuwamba.
