An shirya don Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, masu goyon baya na yau da dare na iya zuwa daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a yi amfani da su a cikin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ya ce.
