Almanac: Mahaliccin Geiger Counter
Wannan shi ne shafi daga "Sunday Morning" Almanac: Satumba 30, 1882, 136 zuwa yau, kuma BA BA... ranar haihuwar masanin lissafi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta ganowa da kuma auna kwayoyin halitta, wanda aka kirkira kayan aiki daga wannan wanda aka sani da Geiger Counter.
A cikin kimiyya, Geiger Counter ya kasance mai mahimmanci a cikin al'adun gargajiya, musamman ma a cikin fim din 1950 Bells of Coronado, wanda ya nuna cewa Roy Rogers da Dale Evans sun kasance masu ilimin kimiyya:
Mutum: Mece ce wannan?
Rogers: Giger Counter, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano abubuwa masu guba, kamar sulfur.
Idan ka yi amfani da waɗannan maganganu, za ka ji tasirin kwayoyin halittar da ke faruwa a cikin kwayoyin halitta a cikin kwayoyin halitta.
Evans: "Ya riga ya fashe!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a 1945, jim kadan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma alfarwa wadda take ɗauke da sunansa tana da rai har abada.
Sabon rigakafin cutar kansa na iya sa tsarin garkuwar jikinmu ya koyi yadda ake kashe kwayoyin halitta.
Magungunan rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikin mutum ya gano kwayoyin halitta kuma ya kashe su.
Kwayar cutar ta rigakafi tana nazarin tsarin rigakafi don gane kwayoyin halitta a cikin maganin.
Wannan ya hada da karɓar ƙwayoyin cuta daga mai haƙuri, wanda aka yi amfani da shi a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Bayan haka, an gano cewa sunadarai sun fi dacewa da cututtukan daji da yawa kuma an sake yin allurar rigakafi.
Wani rigakafin gwaji yana nuna sakamako a kan marasa lafiya da kuma masu cutar kansa.
Wata mata da aka yi mata allurar rigakafi, wadda ke nazarin tsarin garkuwar jikin mutum don gano kwayoyin halitta, ta ga ciwon daji na mahaifa ya yi ta raguwa fiye da watanni 18.
Wannan hanya ta hada da cire kwayoyin cuta daga mai haƙuri, kuma a ware su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don gano wani furotin da ya saba da cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtuka da ake kira HER2, sannan kuma a sake harba kwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Cibiyar Ciwon Cutar Kasa ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland ya ce: "Sakamako na mu ya nuna cewa maganin zai iya zama rigakafi mai tasiri sosai".
