Washington na iya amfani da Yakin tekun ta idan ya dace don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwannin, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Ryan Zinke, a cewar Washington Examiner.
