An sake buɗe sabon tsarin Jamus
An tsara sabon tsarin yaki na Yakin Yammacin Jamus a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin tsarin yaki na lokacin Cold War, amma ba zai yiwu ba a wannan shekarar saboda rashin tsari da kuma tsada, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
An dakatar da umarnin "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin saman Baden-Wuerttemberg na zamani, don farkon rabin 2019, kamar yadda jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito wani ma'aikacin soja.
An yi niyyar shigar da jirgin a cikin SeaTree a shekarar 2014 amma matsaloli bayan fitowar sun kawo cikas ga wannan babban aikin jirgin ruwa.
A cikin 2007 an ba da umarnin jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da ke da jirgin ruwa na Maritime, wanda ya maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Bayanai sun nuna cewa akwai wani abu mai karfi mai karfi, nau'ikan fashewar fashewa da fashewar fashewa da kuma wasu fasahohin zamani, kamar su radiation, siginar sararin samaniya da kuma zamani.
Sauran muhimman abubuwan da suka faru sune tsawon lokaci a cikin matsakaicin lokaci - wanda ke nufin cewa jiragen ruwa na iya tashi har tsawon shekaru biyu daga tashar jiragen sama na gida.
Amma, sakamakon irin wannan ƙwarewar, yawancin fasahohin zamani sun zama tsofaffi - ana iya cewa Jamus za ta iya nuna abin da take da shi a ƙasashen waje - kuma an gabatar da su don amfani, Die Zeit ya ce.
An yi ta yin ta'aziyya sosai game da motar F125 mai wahala a wannan shekarar, lokacin da Hukumar Kula da Jiragen Ruwa ta Jamus ta sake fasalin motar kuma ta mayar da ita a filin jirgin sama na Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da aka mayar da mota ta hanyar mota zuwa wani kamfanin kera motoci bayan an sake shi.
Ba a san ainihin dalilin da ya sa aka mayar da su ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ce suna da "manyan kayan aiki da kayan aiki", kuma saboda haka babu dalilin damuwa idan an tura su zuwa yaki.
Rashin daidaituwa na software yana da mahimmanci lokacin da motocin Baden-Wuerttemberg ke sarrafawa ta hanyar 120 cents - wannan shine rabin mutanen da ake buƙata don sarrafa motocin Bremen.
Duk da haka, an gano cewa motar ta kasance mai nauyi sosai, wanda ya rage yawan aiki da kuma ƙara yawan ƙarfin Tarin Teku don ƙara ƙarin haɓakawa.
An yi zargin cewa "Rheinland-Pfalz" ya ninka nauyin tan 7,000 fiye da irin motocin yaki da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga rashin daidaituwa, duk abin da ke cikin motar - har ma da horar da masu aikin jirgin sama - yana da matsala.
An ce an kai €3.3 biliyan ($3.6bn) - karuwa daga €2.2 biliyan da aka fara.
Matsalar jiragen ruwa na zamani sun zama mafi mahimmanci saboda gargadin kwanan nan cewa sojojin Jamus suna raguwa.
