A cikin wani jawabi a cikin wani bidiyo na Instagram Live ga mabiyansa miliyan 142 bayan zargin da aka yi, Ronaldo, mai shekaru 33, ya yi tir da zargin, yana mai cewa "mai ba da labari ne".
